<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#121212">
    <title>Our Projects - Skypixel</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/logo.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css?v=<%= assetVersion %>">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" media="print" onload="this.media='all'" integrity="sha512-Fo3rlrZj/k7ujTnHg4CGR2D7kSs0v4LLanw2qksYuRlEzO+tcaEPQogQ0KaoGN26/zrn20ImR1DfuLWnOo7aBA==" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body class="has-sticky-footer">
    <div id="loader-wrapper">
        <div class="loader-content">
            <div id="loading-text-animation"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-blur" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div id="main-content">
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="container">
                <a href="/" class="nav-brand">Skypixel</a>
                <a href="/about" class="btn"><i class="fas fa-users"></i> About Us</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <section id="projects" class="projects section-padding fade-in-scroll">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Projects</h2>

                <div class="project-category category-popular">
                    <div class="category-header">
                        <h3>Most Popular</h3>
                        <p>Where our biggest communities gather and rely on Skypixel tools every single day.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project-grid">
                        <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll">
                            <img src="/images/project1.jpg" alt="Project 1 - Puro" loading="lazy" decoding="async" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/202020/e0e0e0?text=Image+Error';">
                            <div class="project-card-content">
                                <div>
                                    <span class="project-status status-popular">Most Popular</span>
                                    <h3>Puro</h3>
                                    <p>Puro is a versatile Discord bot designed to enhance member interaction and provide robust moderation tools to secure your Discord server effectively.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="project-buttons">
                                    <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="1"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                    <a href="https://github.com/norbertbaricz/Puro/releases" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download</a>
                                    <span class="btn btn-secondary disabled" role="button" aria-disabled="true" tabindex="-1"><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> Feedback</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
                            <img src="/images/project3.jpg" alt="Project 3 - Server Launcher" loading="lazy" decoding="async" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/202020/e0e0e0?text=Image+Error';">
                            <div class="project-card-content">
                                <div>
                                    <span class="project-status status-popular">Most Popular</span>
                                    <h3>Server Launcher</h3>
                                    <p>The Server Launcher is a user-friendly Windows application designed to simplify the management of your home-hosted Minecraft server, making server administration straightforward and efficient.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="project-buttons">
                                    <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="3"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                    <a href="https://github.com/norbertbaricz/Server-Launcher/releases" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download</a>
                                    <span class="btn btn-secondary disabled" role="button" aria-disabled="true" tabindex="-1"><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> Feedback</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="project-category category-new">
                    <div class="category-header">
                        <h3>New Release</h3>
                        <p>Fresh launches that showcase what the Skypixel lab has been building lately.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project-grid">
                        <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                            <img src="/images/project4.jpg" alt="Skypixel Website Project" loading="lazy" decoding="async" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/202020/e0e0e0?text=Image+Error';">
                            <div class="project-card-content">
                                <div>
                                    <span class="project-status status-new">New Release</span>
                                    <h3>Skypixel Website</h3>
                                    <p>Welcome to the Skypixel website! Here, you can explore all our exciting projects and get to know the talented team behind the innovations. Dive in and discover what Skypixel has to offer!</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="project-buttons">
                                    <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="4"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                    <a href="https://github.com/norbertbaricz/Skypixel/releases" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download</a>
                                    <span class="btn btn-secondary disabled" role="button" aria-disabled="true" tabindex="-1"><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> Feedback</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
                            <img src="/images/project5.jpg" alt="Project BoosterX" loading="lazy" decoding="async" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/202020/e0e0e0?text=Image+Error';">
                            <div class="project-card-content">
                                <div>
                                    <span class="project-status status-new">New Release</span>
                                    <h3>BoosterX</h3>
                                    <p>BoosterX is a state-of-the-art optimization tool designed to maximize your system's performance and ensure a smoother, more responsive experience.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="project-buttons">
                                    <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="5"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary disabled"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download</a>
                                    <span class="btn btn-secondary disabled" role="button" aria-disabled="true" tabindex="-1"><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> Feedback</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="project-category category-eol">
                    <div class="category-header">
                        <h3>EOL (End Of Life)</h3>
                        <p>Legacy builds we’ve sunset—still available as archives for servers that need them.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project-grid">
                        <div class="project-card fade-in-scroll" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                            <img src="/images/project2.jpg" alt="Project 2 - DakotaAC" loading="lazy" decoding="async" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/600x400/202020/e0e0e0?text=Image+Error';">
                            <div class="project-card-content">
                                <div>
                                    <span class="project-status status-eol">End of Life</span>
                                    <h3>DakotaAC</h3>
                                    <p>DakotaAC reached its final release, but the archive remains for server owners who still need the classic Minecraft anti-cheat toolkit.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="project-buttons">
                                    <a href="#" class="btn" data-project="2"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Details</a>
                                    <a href="https://github.com/norbertbaricz/DakotaAC/releases" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fas fa-archive"></i> Archive</a>
                                    <span class="btn btn-secondary disabled" role="button" aria-disabled="true" tabindex="-1"><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i> Feedback</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <div id="project-popup" class="popup">
            <div class="popup-content project">
                <span class="close-btn">&times;</span>
                <div class="project-popup-grid">
                    <img id="project-image" alt="Project image" />
                    <div class="project-popup-meta">
                        <h2 id="popup-project-title">Project Details</h2>
                        <p class="project-tag" id="popup-project-tag"></p>
                        <p id="project-description">Default project description text if not overridden by JS.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="sticky-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 Skypixel. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
    <script defer src="/js/script.js?v=<%= assetVersion %>"></script><script defer src="/js/projects-script.js?v=<%= assetVersion %>"></script> </body>
</html>
